rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：Otto 辛宝、TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Whiskey Web and Whatnot：人类成「遗留依赖」</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Robbie 和 Adam 边喝 High 'n Wicked 黑麦边聊：Agent 工作流兴起后，人类是否正在变成自己系统里的「遗留依赖」。涉及 OpenClaw 的搭建体验、Pi 的极简 Agent 哲学（bash 优先于 MCP）、可塑性软件、SaaS 股价为何崩盘，以及 MoltBook、RentAHuman.ai、Polymarket 与 meme coin、AI Agent 在社交媒体上互相对话等话题，信息量很足的一期。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-wo